snippet.title: Bollygrad Studioz
snippet.description: BFTI is a registered organisation under the banner of Bhashahome Services India LLP, which facilitates the performing arts enthusiasts under the guidance of professionals of various wizardries. Right from the acting to various forms of dances, imbibing the detailed minutiae of singing to train the nuances of instrumental music, BFTI professionals impart the creative education to the aspirants.
